snippet: Emails released by the House Energy and Commerce Committee open a window into the negotiations between the White House, Senate Democrats and pharmaceutical industry in 2009 as part of President Obama’s drive to overhaul the health care system.
lead_paragraph: Emails released by the House Energy and Commerce Committee open a window into the negotiations between the White House, Senate Democrats and pharmaceutical industry in 2009 as part of President Obama’s drive to overhaul the health care system.
